%% Data Flow Diagram - Data Science Pipelines Tekton
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ds-pipeline API<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Tekton as Tekton Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod
    participant MinIO as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant MySQL as MariaDB/MySQL<br/>3306/TCP
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SW as Scheduled Workflow Controller
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    OAuthProxy->>UI: HTTP/3000<br/>Authenticated
    UI->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>kubeflow-userid header
    API->>MySQL: MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password<br/>Store pipeline metadata
    API->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount token<br/>Create PipelineRun
    K8sAPI->>Tekton: Reconcile PipelineRun
    Tekton->>Pod: Schedule Pipeline Pod
    Pod->>MinIO: HTTP/9000<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey<br/>Store artifacts
    PA->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount token<br/>Watch PipelineRun/TaskRun
    K8sAPI-->>PA: PipelineRun status updates
    PA->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Sync run status

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Scheduled Workflow Execution

    User->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>kubeflow-userid header<br/>Create recurring job
    API->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Create ScheduledWorkflow CR
    SW->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Watch ScheduledWorkflow
    K8sAPI-->>SW: ScheduledWorkflow CR events
    SW->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Create PipelineRun (on schedule)

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: ML Metadata Tracking

    MW->>Envoy: gRPC/9090<br/>No encryption<br/>Write execution metadata
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC/8080<br/>Forward request
    MLMD->>MySQL: MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password<br/>Persist metadata
